Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the control flow for the APRConfig system:

```plantuml
@startuml DehengYang_APRConfig

actor User
participant "Run_d4j_1.py" as Main
participant "Config" as Config
participant "DatasetFactory" as DatasetFactory
participant "Defects4j" as Dataset
participant "LocalizerFactory" as LocalizerFactory
participant "Gzoltar" as Localizer
participant "AprFactory" as AprFactory
participant "AprTool" as AprTool
participant "Main_parse.py" as Parser

User -> Main: Execute
activate Main

Main -> Config: Load configuration
activate Config
Config --> Main: Configuration loaded
deactivate Config

Main -> DatasetFactory: Create dataset
activate DatasetFactory
DatasetFactory -> Dataset: Initialize
activate Dataset
Dataset --> DatasetFactory: Dataset ready
DatasetFactory --> Main: Dataset instance
deactivate DatasetFactory

Main -> LocalizerFactory: Create localizer
activate LocalizerFactory
LocalizerFactory -> Localizer: Initialize
activate Localizer
Localizer --> LocalizerFactory: Localizer ready
LocalizerFactory --> Main: Localizer instance
deactivate LocalizerFactory

Main -> Dataset: Get bugs
activate Dataset
Dataset --> Main: Bug list
deactivate Dataset

loop For each bug
    Main -> Dataset: Checkout bug
    activate Dataset
    Dataset --> Main: Bug checked out
    deactivate Dataset

    Main -> Localizer: Localize fault
    activate Localizer
    Localizer --> Main: Suspicious statements
    deactivate Localizer

    Main -> AprFactory: Create APR tool
    activate AprFactory
    AprFactory -> AprTool: Initialize
    activate AprTool
    AprTool --> AprFactory: APR tool ready
    AprFactory --> Main: APR tool instance
    deactivate AprFactory

    Main -> AprTool: Generate patches
    activate AprTool
    AprTool --> Main: Generated patches
    deactivate AprTool

    loop For each patch
        Main -> Dataset: Apply patch
        activate Dataset
        Dataset --> Main: Patch applied
        deactivate Dataset

        Main -> Dataset: Run tests
        activate Dataset
        Dataset --> Main: Test results
        deactivate Dataset

        alt Patch fixes bug
            Main -> Dataset: Record successful patch
            activate Dataset
            Dataset --> Main: Patch recorded
            deactivate Dataset
        else Patch fails
            Main -> Dataset: Revert patch
            activate Dataset
            Dataset --> Main: Patch reverted
            deactivate Dataset
        end
    end
end

Main -> Parser: Parse repair data
activate Parser
Parser --> Main: CSV output
deactivate Parser

Main --> User: Execution complete
deactivate Main

@enduml
```

This sequence diagram illustrates the control flow of the APRConfig system, showing the interactions between the main components during the automated program repair process.